    <item>
      <title>黑石集团将向意大利公司提供超过 2.5 亿欧元的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/blackstone-set-to-provide-over-250-million-debt-to-italian-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私人信贷基金管理公司黑石公司 (Blackstone Inc.) 即将达成一项协议，提供超过 2.5 亿欧元（3.29 亿美元）的债务方案，为 Wateralia SpA 的现有债务进行再融资，这是意大利借款人向直接贷款人寻求融资的最新例子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/blackstone-set-to-provide-over-250-million-debt-to-italian-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 11:10:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街认为国防类股还有进一步上涨的空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/wall-street-sees-more-room-for-defense-stocks-torrid-advance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[地缘政治紧张局势加剧时，押注国防供应商至少在短期内会获得回报，这已不是什么秘密。但华尔街表示，最新一轮涨势背后还有更多原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/wall-street-sees-more-room-for-defense-stocks-torrid-advance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 11:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴黎小麦期货因与黑海作物竞争而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/paris-wheat-futures-slide-in-bid-to-compete-with-black-sea-crops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场寻求有竞争力的价格来吸引主要买家从廉价的黑海作物中回归，巴黎小麦期货连续第四天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/paris-wheat-futures-slide-in-bid-to-compete-with-black-sea-crops</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:42:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国市场警告习近平需要更多刺激措施来推动经济反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-markets-warn-xi-that-more-stimulus-is-needed-to-fuel-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从国家主席习近平上个月试图为中国经济放缓划上句号以来，投资者一直强烈要求他采取强有力的财政刺激措施，支持货币宽松政策，以推动中国股市出现多年来最大的涨势之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-markets-warn-xi-that-more-stimulus-is-needed-to-fuel-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 09:45:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vasle 称欧洲央行下周降息并不能保证 12 月利率变动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ecb-cut-next-week-wouldn-t-guarantee-december-move-vasle-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员波斯扬·瓦斯莱 (Bostjan Vasle) 表示，10 月份降低利率并不意味着欧洲央行一定会在今年最后一次会议上再次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ecb-cut-next-week-wouldn-t-guarantee-december-move-vasle-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 08:56:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于中国未能推出新的刺激措施，金属价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/iron-ore-pushes-higher-as-chinese-markets-reopen-after-holiday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国最高经济规划师备受期待的发布会结束后，铁矿石价格从五个月高点暴跌，基本金属价格也出现下跌，但发布会结束时，中国并未做出增加政府支出的新承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/iron-ore-pushes-higher-as-chinese-markets-reopen-after-holiday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 00:46:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场焦点转向通胀数据，美国期货上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股指期货上涨，扭转了早前的跌势，因为交易员将注意力转向本周晚些时候公布的通胀数据，以判断美联储的利率走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 22:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
